Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:02.69,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As bright as a spark,\Nwith a sharp and precise wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:04.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once he gets started,\Nyou can't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:06.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Summer vacation's only just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:08.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What kind of guy has\NSonoko taken a liking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:10.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.78,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:15.03,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:56.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}At the beach in Izu, Ran and I\Nwitnessed a strange summer event!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:02:00.98,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Somehow, Sonoko got herself a boyfriend by the name of Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:04.55,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But while Sonoko's\Nin seventh heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:08.10,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}waiting for Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10} to\Npick her up for their dinner date,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.42,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}someone attacked her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:19.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Am I imagining things,\Nor does this guy keep watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:24.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then there's that guy in the glasses who Ran thinks she's seen somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:28.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And as for the guy\Nwho attacked Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:34.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was he really just a simple thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:55.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a lovely restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There don't seem to be\Nmany customers, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we came too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you\Naren't coming, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I kept remembering that guy last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep much,\Nso I'm going to sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.\NBut what a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, there are drinks in this cooler,\Nso help yourself whenever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll see you later, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, if you're feeling up to it\Nafter your nap, join us in the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't stay up another minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seafood here is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a shame, since I wanted to let Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think she'll be all right?\NShe's sleeping inside a hot car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I turned\Nthe air conditioner on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at this!\NIs this for one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's plenty\Nand the price is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the secret to\Nthis restaurant's popularity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:26.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh geez. A full-course\Nmeal for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? Didn't I tell you\Nthe food was great?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm completely stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel a bit bad\Nfor Sonoko though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're from the inn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's your\Nbrown-haired friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen her anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems she's\Na bit sleep-deprived,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she's resting in\Nthe car parked outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that your car, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why's it moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad! It's heading\Nstraight for the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where do you think\Nyou're going? Pay your bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's a lockpick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The hand brake's disengaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, wake up! Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't put full strength in\Nwhile I'm running!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!\NWe're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nget away from the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, grab onto me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NAre you guys all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was close.\NI'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you put\Nthe hand brake on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!\NI {\i1}did{\i0} have it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:07:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it weren't on, the car would've\Nfallen off the cliff a lot sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone released the hand brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:10.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone broke into the car\Nusing a lockpick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who was after\NSonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So someone broke into the car\Nwhile Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was asleep inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,released the hand brake,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and made the car roll down\Nthis slope and off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the diver's report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hand brake of the car underwater\Nwas disengaged, just as we suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, we found this lying on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lockpick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with a pro here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been wiped clean of prints!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find any other clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a puddle of water that must've\Nleaked out of the car's air conditioner
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where the car was parked\Nin the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, did you notice any\Nsuspicious figures around the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep much last night,\Nso I was sound asleep in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But ever since we arrived in Izu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,someone suspicious has been\Ntailing us for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's him over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon my rudeness,\Nbut could you identify yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I work at the inn where\Nthe girls are staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inn's not busy\Nduring the afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I had some free time,\Nso I came here today to have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He isn't behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:51.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When the car started moving, he was\Nalready in the restaurant with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he'd forced the car door open,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:59.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}released the hand brake,\Nand then come into the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:04.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}we would have seen him\Ncome in through the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:10.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When I asked the waiter, he told me\Nthat the back door is always kept locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:14.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We first noticed him when\Nhe came out of the restroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:18.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but there's no window leading out\Nfrom inside that restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:22.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And of course, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s\Nin the clear too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:28.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He was eating with us\Nand never left the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:34.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The most likely suspect is\Nthe man who's been following us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is he anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll take all your statements\Ndown at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please get into the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Umm, I don't feel like\Nriding in a car right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about I walk you\Nto the police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that far, and we can\Nenjoy the scenery. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if she gets attacked again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} does have\Nbrown hair, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her assailant could also be\Nthe same killer from that other case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would be foolish enough to attack her in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But you never know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will be with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if worse comes\Nto worst, so will Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just don't stop anywhere.\NCome straight to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The attack at the inn last night,\Nand then the car incident today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sure are after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, are you sure you don't\Nhave any idea what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because\Nyou're so charming?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:10.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Right, why is she being targeted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:17.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And if he was after her life, why didn't\Nhe do it when he broke into the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:24.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There was no need to put the car in gear\Nand have it plunge off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we planned on going home as soon\Nas we had lunch at the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so all of our luggage\Nwas in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all gone up in flames now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, why do we have to\Nbe put through all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yours is nothing in comparison!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I lost my car!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because you got\Ninvolved with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I brought you bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. That's not right, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing compared to losing\Nall the memorable photos you took.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Photos are something\Nyou can never replace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that's left now\Nis that one photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, the one I'm going\Nto show Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have it on me at all times—\Nyou have nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still have it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, get rid of it!\NYou're making me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it!\NIt's that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:18.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm certain the killer wants\Nto get rid of that photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:23.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's why he had to send the car\Nover the cliff to get rid of Sonoko's luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:32.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why does he think Sonoko took\Nan incriminating picture of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:38.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There wasn't a single unusual\Nphoto in the ones she took.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:43.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or did I overlook something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:54.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we're being followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it more dangerous\Nto go through the woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is more thrilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's split up\Nto shake him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:40.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he's Sonoko's attacker,\Nwhy's he still after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:42.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All the photos were burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:48.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A train?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:52.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, they found\Na body in this forest yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:57.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When we passed this place a couple\Nnights ago, I'm sure a train went by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:03.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm missing something here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! I've lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The situation's turning bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you thought we'd just run,\Nyou've made a big mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Owowowowow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have run\Nthrough the forest in sandals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sandals?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who attacked\NSonoko last night at the inn,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and sent the car over the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on there! That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No use lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your hairy arms\Nare proof enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There should be bite marks\Nwhere Sonoko bit you last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...\NThere's no bite marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe on the other arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? No marks on\Nthis arm either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:13.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective with the Chiba\NPrefecture Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just showing me the cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're dead wrong if you think\NI'd fall for that trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father used to be a police\Nofficer. You can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When an officer has to\Nidentify him or herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they must show the first page\Nof the police notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the photo\Nand corresponding data.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name's Shoji Terabayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.\NIt's the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm on the trail of a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't usually wear\Nsocks with sandals, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:54.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stepped on a twig.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess running about in the forest\Nwith sandals wasn't such a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:08.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tooth marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be so\Nsurprised about, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the mark\Nyou gave me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:37.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So {\i1}that's{\i0} it!\NThat's what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:41.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko didn't bite his arm\Nlast night—she bit his leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She must've gotten\Nmixed up in the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:47.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He probably thought\NSonoko took his picture
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:51.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}because the sparks the\Ntrain's pantograph produces
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}lit him from behind\Nat the time of the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:58.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And seeing Sonoko, who passed by\Nholding a camera immediately after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he jumped to\Nthe wrong conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He thought he'd\Nbeen seen with the victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:06.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it,\NI remember him saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:11.85,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't worry. You look\Ngood in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yukata, swimsuit, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:18.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The only time Sonoko wore a yukata was\Nduring the fireworks show two nights ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We only met him yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:23.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He wouldn't have known\Nwhat she looks like in a yukata!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:25.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! Why didn't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why didn't I figure it out sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The picture you were going to\Nhave some detective look at!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably planned on taking\Na romantic picture of a couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that photo shows me in the\Nmiddle of committing murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like I am now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} killed four people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was responsible for\Nthe murder the other night,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then she's probably the fourth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, he only\Nkills girls with brown hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've had my eyes on\Nhim for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got him on a stolen\Nvehicle charge once,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there wasn't enough\Nproof on the murder charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to Izu because I heard that\Na similar murder happened here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and here he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I arrived too late\Nto save his latest victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's something\NI still don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did he make the car move on its own\Nif he was in the restaurant the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took a wedge-shaped\Npiece of ice out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and placed it under the left front tire\Nto prevent it from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he pretended to talk to\NSonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} who was inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and released the hand brake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he left a\Nlockpick on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to divert the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he left two\Nspaces open when he parked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there'd be no cars obstructing\Nhis car's path when it moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, the melted ice would\Njust appear to be water from the AC.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:06.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why does he kill only\Ngirls with brown hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?\NA heartless girl dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's... That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever I see flirty girls like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially when I see girls with brown hair,\Njust like the one who dumped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look over there!\NIsn't that Sonoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:30.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why are all the guys that\Nmake a play for me so weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:41.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I hate you, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Am {\i1}I{\i0} all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd seen that guy\Nwith the glasses before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was at the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the captain of the Haido\NHigh School Karate Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Prince of Kicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto Kyogoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:25.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a very reckless lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lucky I was nearby\Nand had some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Free time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mean you were\Nfollowing me all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was following you\Nthe whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I lost sight\Nof you in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew you might mistake\Nme for a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'd been flirting\Nwith a few other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It got me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you worry about me?\NYou don't even know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably didn't notice me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I'd seen you once before,\Nat a karate tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were cheering on your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd\Nreserve a room in our inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to recommend that,\Nas much possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you avoid wearing those lingerie-like outfits that arouse men.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you're free\Nto ignore my advice,
