Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and he were getting along\Nso well since then, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he ran out of strong opponents\Nin Japan, so he went abroad to train.
