Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go see the baseball team's practice game!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other team's ace is a\Nfirst-year high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear he's so cute\Nand just so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to wait\Nfor Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's that, this is this!
