Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.62,0:24:15.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:19.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no way a person\Ncould come in through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.29,0:24:24.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just what trick was used to\Nturn this into a locked room?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.77,0:24:30.80,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
